<br>
The goblin traitor can be found next to a tent at the west side of the &quot;Goblin City&quot; in Droga. This is the area where the Shroud of Nature drops. He is on Chardok faction, which means that if you are still KoS to the Brood of Di'zok, you may kill him without noticing! Beware.<br>
<br>
The angry goblin spawns in the tunnel to the south-east of the Chief's room. As far as I know, he is indifferent to all. (When I did my turnin for Ring 2, I had a couple players who were KoS in Chardok, and he was indiff to them.)<br>
<br>
...<br>
