<br>
2. Park your pet there.<br>
<br>
3. Find a safe place to SIT and plant your butt.<br>
<br>
4. Make sure you have an escape handy (zone or gate or whatever, and turn up the volume so you can hear if something jumps ya.<br>
<br>
5. Hang out as long as needed <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I know this works, and I know you can get faction hits across a zone since I did this in Warsilks Woods to get Cablis faction with the bandits while I was hunting for Gracknist ?sp? (stupid thing hasn't dropped an earring in 30 kills).<br>
<br>
Other things to note:<br>
<br>
You really need a clear spot to hang out as you must be sitting for the mobs to agro on your pet without you there. Somehow the sitting agro must carry over through your pet.<br>
<br>
